div.p: On x86_64, clock_gettime(CLOCK_MONOTONIC) uses the vDSO (virtual Dynamic Shared Object).

ul.li: Reads TSC (Time Stamp Counter) directly from CPU.

div.p: Result: T2 < T1 elapsed: -50,000,000 ns CRITICAL FAILURE: Timestamps move backwards
Result: T2 > T1 elapsed: +50,000,000 ns GUARANTEED progression
